FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775221865
OL,3,C'It's a bit mad': Man's 183 mile run
OL,4,Cto save a life
OL,6,FThat is a total of 183 miles,
OL,7,Finvolving a lot of laps of Ormeau Park
OL,8,Fand a whole lot of willpower. When
OL,9,Fasked if people might think he is
OL,10,F"mad" for taking this on, he said: "I
OL,11,Fam. I didn't think when I started this
OL,12,Fout that it was quite mad,"
OL,14,F"But the more training I've done, the
OL,15,Fmore I've spoke to people who are more
OL,16,Fexperienced runners than I am. I think
OL,17,Fit's a bit mad."
OL,19,FConor is fuelled by his past.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775221865
OL,3,C'It's a bit mad': Man's 183 mile run
OL,4,Cto save a life
OL,6,FHaving attempted to take his own life
OL,7,F12 years ago, he understands how far
OL,8,Fhe has come. He is now hoping to raise
OL,9,Fawareness and money for charity to
OL,10,Fhelp those less fortunate than him.
OL,12,F"I've kind of come out of that dark
OL,13,Fplace that I was in," Conor said. "I
OL,14,Fthought there was no other charity
OL,15,Fthat I would rather do it for than a
OL,16,Fmental health charity."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775221865
OL,3,C'It's a bit mad': Man's 183 mile run
OL,4,Cto save a life
OL,6,FHe added: "I would rather me go
OL,7,Fthrough it than someone else, but it
OL,8,Fhas taught me so much. I'm a much more
OL,9,Fwell-rounded person, I'm probably a
OL,10,Flot more humble."
OL,12,FConor was able to win the race against
OL,13,Fhis mind, and his message for those
OL,14,Fsuffering is simple, "talk more and
OL,15,Fmove more."
OL,17,FHe credits his recovery to a
OL,18,Fcombination of professional help and
OL,19,Fphysical discipline.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
