PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775221865
OL,3,C'It's a bit mad': Man's 183 mile run
OL,4,Cto save a life
OL,6,F"First step was honestly just
OL,7,Ftalking," he said. "I went to a
OL,8,Ftherapy session once and I came out
OL,9,Fdancing and singing, and it was my
OL,10,Ffirst one. Getting that therapy that
OL,11,Fyou need and telling someone your
OL,12,Fproblems, it takes a weight off your
OL,13,Fshoulders.
OL,15,F"I got into a structure, I got into a
OL,16,Froutine, and that was the best therapy
OL,17,Ffor me. You train for the mind and the
OL,18,Fbody will kind of look after itself,
OL,19,Fand it's so true.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
