PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775221865
OL,3,C'It's a bit mad': Man's 183 mile run
OL,4,Cto save a life
OL,6,F"The thought of the run is always so
OL,7,Fmuch worse than the run itself. Rain,
OL,8,Fhail, snow. Get the shoes on, get to a
OL,9,Flocal park, get out and run."
